      "point": "Insufficient reproducibility details for UniFew baseline and sample size design parameters",
      "evidence": "The full reproducibility might be hindered by a lack of granular detail regarding the specific pre-trained UniFew model (UniﬁedQA)... The summary lacks the granular details of these simulation studies."
