    {
      "point": "Unjustified episode sampling strategy",
      "evidence": "A uniform distribution of shots between 1 and 5 (i.e., 1-shot, 2-shot, 3-shot, 4-shot, 5-shot) might not accurately represent the most critical or common few-shot scenarios."
